Some code found within this project does originate from a great external project
known as Prism.  You can find this project here:
https://github.com/PrismLibrary/Prism

All code in this project that makes use of this originating code is subject to
and copyrighted under the conditions of the license found here:
https://github.com/PrismLibrary/Prism/blob/master/LICENSE

The code here is borrowed as Prism owners did not want to change the 
intent/concern/location of its modularity, logging, eventing and bootstrapping
functionality.  This project has does this and has adapted these features here
accordingly.

More information about this can be found at these locations:
https://github.com/PrismLibrary/Prism/issues/3
https://github.com/PrismLibrary/Prism/issues/4
https://github.com/PrismLibrary/Prism/issues/1